title: Check list for RB101 written assesment prepÂ

cells.data:
finish taking notes on all the lessons (IMPORTANT: Review notes not finished)

 make a check list from the study guide 

 Pass through study good and insure you have a good understanding of all the items in the study guide (write check list for this)

 go through all the articles recommend in the study guide and take detailed notes on these

 create a reference sheet with mark down to use doing the test 
    create can sentences to used and a list of key words (local variable, constant, initialized etc)

Complete all problems in this study guide (https://github.com/ryanschaul/101_programming_foundations/blob/master/assessment1_prep.md)

Complete all all of Sardens study guide series (https://medium.com/how-i-started-learning-coding-from-scratch/advices-for-109-written-assessment-part-1-6f7fa821cf84)
